data.title: Kodak Film Order & Catalogue - Buy Kodak Film
data.meta_description: Price catalogs and information on how to order KODAK Motion Picture Film
data.text:
Email your order to EIAmericas@kodak.com and include:

Outline of your order

Purchase Order number where applicable

"Ship to" information

Kodak account number where applicable

Customers paying by credit card must call KODAK Customer Service at 1-800-356-3259 8 a.m.-5 p.m. ET, Monday-Friday to arrange for payment

Note: Anticipated delivery will be five (5) working days after the date of your order.

Expedited delivery may be available for an extra charge.
